title: WTB: N172 Milwaukee Player Cards (Maybe N284 too)
author: AdamG

posts.post_title: WTB: N172 Milwaukee Player Cards (Maybe N284 too)
posts.post_content:
I'm looking for some N172 and maybe N284 Milwaukee player cards. I'm interested in mainly raw, ungraded cards.

I'd prefer nice eye appeal but I don't care about minor trimming... I generally avoid major front paper loss and large card length creases.

Sadly I don't have anything to trade... I'm just looking to get a couple specimens to get my collection going. I only have one of each type in very poor condition.

Thanks!
